How to use TinkerCAD :
1. After logging in to Tinkercad, click on "Circuits" on the left-hand side. 
2. Then "Create New Circuit" homepage in Tinkercad. 
3. Start by adding the Arduino UNO to your design. 
4. Add the additional components to the circuit design. 
5. Add connections between the components.
6. Write the code(text) or use blocks to the circuit
7. And simulate (play).
8. Sense the results.
